data.description: Don't miss this stylish 3 bedroom 2 bath home in desirable Suntree.  Nestled within manicured landscaping, this stunning pool home offers a perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and leisure. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space with a seated island. Whether you're entertaining guests or preparing a quiet meal for yourself, this kitchen is a perfect blend of style and functionality.   French doors off the generously sized primary suite allow private access to the pool area with view to the fairways.  The two additional bedrooms provide comfort and privacy in this split plan, perfect for a growing family or accommodating guests. Whole house hurricane shutters. Kitchen and baths renovated 2019.  New roof 2019.  New irrigation pump July 2021.  New Lennox Signature Series AC/dehumidifier and pool pump Late 2021. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and top-rated schools, this property seamlessly combines the tranquility of a golf course lifestyle with the convenience of city living. Don't miss the opportunity to call this spectacular home your own in the heart of Suntree!
